Class Automobile

  • java.lang.Object
    • Automobile
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Movable
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    Car, Truck
    public abstract class Automobile
extends java.lang.Object
implements Movable
    A class for Automobiles. Contains necessary methods to make a Automobile move (speed up, slow down, turn). Assumes "forward" is up.
